{"id":619251,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【cdtv】《南方公园》第23季弟2集-band-in-china/","date":"2019-10-06T05:31:40Z","modified":"2019-10-06T05:40:55Z","title":"【CDTV】《南方公园》第23季第2集——Band In China","content":"<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">俩个小时糙翻了一下南方公园s23e02，其实我不会做字幕，这是第一次搞，这集实在是太爆炸了给不会英文的朋友享用，二老的水平有点回归了呢<a href=\"https://t.co/LTJtyGBCcx\">https://t.co/LTJtyGBCcx</a> 找了个匿名网盘发布，希望大家帮我转发一下 这集值得你国人真的应该仔细品味一番</p>\n<p>&mdash; 84之春 (@84springcome) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/84springcome/status/1180107940776165376?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 4, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\">👏 <a href=\"https://t.co/uOHBheJyyG\">https://t.co/uOHBheJyyG</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 84之春 (@84springcome) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/84springcome/status/1180649371269943296?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 6, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>来源：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/6013\">品葱网友 lelouchgreat</a></p>\n<p>用推上@84springcome的字幕重新校对润色修改了一些翻译错误后压制的1080P片源</p>\n<p>在线：</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"SP S23E02 1080P CN\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/sWDzbEnO5C4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"sp_s23e02_1080p_cn\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/364466721?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>网盘：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1t3SGOkwxvxixtCQSIZHrHX2JX88sCPer/view\">google drive</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://oload.monster/f/Y5z43ag8_UA/sp_s23e02_1080p_cn.mp4\">openload</a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p>香港01 | South Park 最新一集《Band in China》被禁讨论S23E02成敏感词</p>\n<p><strong>港称《衰仔乐园》的美国卡通《South Park》，一向以抵死烂口见称，最新一集《Band in China》讲述主角一班人组成的金属乐队要到「China」发展，却遭到政府监控创作及强行改造成男团，这一集仲有小熊维尼出现在监狱之中。</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_619252\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-619252\" class=\"wp-image-619252\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec.jpg 1600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec-300x210.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec-768x538.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec-1024x717.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec-1080x757.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-619252\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">最新一集South Park 《Band in China》讲述有角色想在中国发大财，却遇不到同的「遭遇」。(图片来源： South Park Studio 网站截图)</p></div>\n<p>South Park 今集《Band in China》主要分为两条故事线，在美国种植大麻的Randy (港译：子祥，因他样子像林子祥！) 想到「China」扩展市场，当然他一落机就遭到拘捕，然后他被送往劳改营，在营中他遇到因「样貌」而被监禁的小熊维尼及猪仔，之后他亦遇上希望到「China」做生意，而极度「爱国」的米老鼠，Randy 从中学懂了做生意之道。</p>\n<p>另一方面，Stan 与一众主角成立了一队死亡金属乐队，有经理人带他们冲出South Park，往「China」发展，但因为歌词及风格问题，乐队的创作一直「被指导」，Stan在压迫之下有了新想法打入「China」市场。乐队成员改变风格成为「Finger Band」，即是一些老套，兼会在唱歌时用手指，指来指去的男团。Stan 最后醒觉不能因赚钱，而出卖灵魂，成为护旗男团。</p>\n<p>面对China 市场，Stan 道出一队乐队，应该有的坚持和态度：</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"The Return of Fingerbang - &quot;Band in China&quot; - s23e02 - South Park\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/g6DI6XuvCwE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>在《Band in China》Stan 的死亡金属乐队所演唱的歌曲，是来自真实乐队 Dying Fetus 的作品《Second Skin》。</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"DYING FETUS - &quot;Second Skin&quot; (Official Music Video)\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/H2iiU_Woz-g?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>《Band in China》在中国大陆的反应？</strong></p>\n<p>在视频网站bilibili，之前会有网民非法上载South Park (南方公园) 以往的集数，在《Band in China》推出后，网站积极进行「反侵权」行动，所有相关South Park 的视频一概移除，但在百度贴吧，还可以见到「南方公园吧」，却完全没有关于新一集的讨论，真正做到「Ban in China」。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619253\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0.jpg 1600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0-300x217.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0-768x555.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0-1024x740.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0-1080x781.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>南方公园相关的微信公众号也宣布：所有内容被封禁，公众号被警告，这段时间不再发布任何资源。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGIMAmiU0AAFb2y.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619254\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGIMAmiU0AAFb2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"731\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGIMAmiU0AAFb2y.jpg 630w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGIMAmiU0AAFb2y-185x300.jpg 185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e5%8d%97%e6%96%b9%e5%85%ac%e5%9b%ad-%e5%81%9c%e6%9b%b4%e9%80%9a%e7%9f%a5/\">南方公园 | 停更通知</a></p>\n","author":970,"categories":[18271,38912,38923,38960,38927],"tags":[80,9526,8889,13222,39035,9249,9616,39037,23155,14245]}